  "original_title": "\u2019\u2019\u0d9a\u0dbd\u0dc4\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db1\u0dca \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0d9c\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u2019\u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"Arrest the rioters\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Prime Minister has ordered the security forces to immediately arrest people who behave riotously.",
        "The order states that the vehicles in which rioters are traveling will also be impounded."
      ],
